quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  74,18,"Kanko on, o miijiti o e…ì…ìindii"
  74,19,O hu…óaama hono no o hoddiri
  74,20,Refti o hu…óa hono o hoddiri
  74,21,Refti o ndaari
  74,22,Refti √±ir…ìanii o …ìeydi √±ir…ìinaade
  74,23,Refti o runtii hombo mawnikini
  74,24,"…ìe wi'a: \"∆äum wonaali, si wanaa mbilewu …ìanngu ngu"
  74,25,Mbo wonah si wonah konngol aade
  74,26,Ma Mi naatnu mbo yiite saqara
  74,27,Hol ko anndin ma ko woni Saqara
  74,28,Nge heddatah nge accatah
  74,29,Sumoowe geece
  74,30,Ina e dow mannge sappa e jeenay
  74,31,"Men wa…óaali aynoo…ìe yim…ìe Yiite ngen, si wanaa Malaa'ika. Men wa…óiraali limoore ma…ì…ìe si wanaa jarraborgol yeddu…ìe …ìen, e fii yo henan okkaa…ìe Defte …ìen, e fii no gom…óim…ìe …ìen …ìeydora gom…óinal, e fii wata okkaa…ìe Defte …ìen e gom…óim…ìe …ìen sikkito; e fii yo …ìen …ìe √±awu woni e …ìer…óe mun e heefer…ìe …ìen wi'u: \"Hara ko hon…óum Allah faandorii e ngal misal?\" Ko wano non Allah majjinirta mo O muuyani, himo fewna kadi mo O muuyani. Hay gooto anndaa yeru koneeli Joomi maa …óin, si wanaa Kanko. Ngen [Yiite] wonaali, si wanaa waaju wonannde ne…ó…óanke"
  74,32,Kono yo henane! Mi woondirii lewru ndun
  74,33,O woondiri jemma si mbo runtii ma
  74,34,E subaka si mbo fooyni
  74,35,Ko mbo gootel e maw…ói
  74,36,Ko nge jertinirde wonannde ne…ó…óanke
  74,37,"Wonannde on yi…óu…óo e mo'on, nde o yaccotoo maa nennoo"
  74,38,Wonkii kala ko faggii kon nanngirte
  74,39,Si wanaa yim…ìe √±aamo …ìen
  74,40,"hi…ìe e nder gese, hi…ìe lamndondira"
  74,41,fii bom…ìe …ìen
  74,42,ko ho…óum naadi on Saqara
  74,43,"∆Åen wi'a: \"Men jeyanooka e juuloo…ìe …ìen"
  74,44,men jeyanooka kadi e √±amminoo…ìe miskim…ìe …ìen
  74,45,Hari men jumpidayno kadi e jumpoo…ìe …ìen
  74,46,Hari kadi men fennayno fii √±alaande njo…ìdi nden
  74,47,"Haa [maayde] yananaande nden arani men"
